archimate:BusinessObject.name: MultiLayerSubNetwork
archimate:BusinessObject.documentation: "This object class is an abstraction of the topology provided by the target OS which describes the potential for SubNetwork Connections. Top-level Multi Layer Subnetworks are subnetworks contained directly under either the target OS or a Management Domain. See R_TMF518_NRF_I_0021 and R_TMF518_NRF_I_0021."
